    "body": "This PR adds a new fill benchmark and changes the policy hub to use the vectorized transform kernel for storing when there are no inputs. Some fixes and extensions were made.\r\n\r\nFixes: #5512\r\n\r\nTODO:\r\n\r\n- [x] Tests\r\n- [x] Add a public CUB Fill API, because it's more discoverable than Transform with less inputs\r\n- [x] ~~Compilation time of `cub.test.device_transform.lid_0` \"feels\" to have increased a lot, check this.~~ Instantiating the vector kernel with `huge_t` adds about 11min of compile time. Fortunately, this was a bug and the prefetch kernel should be used.\r\n\r\nBenchmarks are impressive. And we haven't even tuned the kernel.\r\n```\r\n# fill\r\n\r\n## [0] NVIDIA GH200 480GB\r\n\r\n|  T{ct}  |  Elements{io}  |   Ref Time |   Ref Noise |   Cmp Time |   Cmp Noise |        Diff |   %Diff |  Status  |\r\n|---------|----------------|------------|-------------|------------|-------------|-------------|---------|----------|\r\n|   I8    |      2^16      |   3.795 us |       2.55% |   3.631 us |       1.90% |   -0.164 us |  -4.32% |   FAST   |\r\n|   I8    |      2^20      |   5.022 us |       2.90% |   3.883 us |       2.75% |   -1.139 us | -22.68% |   FAST   |\r\n|   I8    |      2^24      |  23.618 us |       0.42% |   7.756 us |       2.69% |  -15.863 us | -67.16% |   FAST   |\r\n|   I8    |      2^28      | 319.103 us |       0.04% |  71.027 us |       0.73% | -248.076 us | -77.74% |   FAST   |\r\n|   I16   |      2^16      |   3.941 us |       2.48% |   3.812 us |       2.46% |   -0.129 us |  -3.27% |   FAST   |\r\n|   I16   |      2^20      |   5.068 us |       2.69% |   4.165 us |       2.96% |   -0.903 us | -17.83% |   FAST   |\r\n|   I16   |      2^24      |  23.587 us |       0.42% |  12.246 us |       2.15% |  -11.341 us | -48.08% |   FAST   |\r\n|   I16   |      2^28      | 319.188 us |       0.04% | 138.661 us |       0.52% | -180.527 us | -56.56% |   FAST   |\r\n|   I32   |      2^16      |   3.929 us |       2.40% |   3.846 us |       2.29% |   -0.083 us |  -2.12% |   SAME   |\r\n|   I32   |      2^20      |   5.073 us |       2.10% |   4.595 us |       3.29% |   -0.479 us |  -9.43% |   FAST   |\r\n|   I32   |      2^24      |  23.772 us |       0.56% |  20.571 us |       1.55% |   -3.201 us | -13.46% |   FAST   |\r\n|   I32   |      2^28      | 319.208 us |       0.05% | 273.917 us |       0.29% |  -45.291 us | -14.19% |   FAST   |\r\n|   I64   |      2^16      |   4.006 us |       2.16% |   3.909 us |       2.93% |   -0.096 us |  -2.40% |   FAST   |\r\n|   I64   |      2^20      |   5.728 us |       2.82% |   5.645 us |       2.59% |   -0.083 us |  -1.45% |   SAME   |\r\n|   I64   |      2^24      |  37.694 us |       1.21% |  37.617 us |       1.06% |   -0.077 us |  -0.20% |   SAME   |\r\n|   I64   |      2^28      | 544.518 us |       0.20% | 544.467 us |       0.19% |   -0.051 us |  -0.01% |   SAME   |\r\n```\r\n\r\n```\r\n# fill\r\n\r\n## [0] NVIDIA GeForce RTX 5090\r\n\r\n|  T{ct}  |  Elements{io}  |   Ref Time |   Ref Noise |   Cmp Time |   Cmp Noise |       Diff |   %Diff |  Status  |\r\n|---------|----------------|------------|-------------|------------|-------------|------------|---------|----------|\r\n|   I8    |      2^16      |   2.819 us |      33.44% |   2.593 us |      33.38% |  -0.226 us |  -8.00% |   SAME   |\r\n|   I8    |      2^20      |   3.996 us |       6.35% |   3.976 us |       7.35% |  -0.020 us |  -0.50% |   SAME   |\r\n|   I8    |      2^24      |  18.349 us |       1.53% |   8.108 us |       3.87% | -10.241 us | -55.81% |   FAST   |\r\n|   I8    |      2^28      | 247.206 us |       0.36% | 158.103 us |       0.79% | -89.102 us | -36.04% |   FAST   |\r\n|   I16   |      2^16      |   3.254 us |      28.11% |   2.808 us |      32.46% |  -0.445 us | -13.69% |   SAME   |\r\n|   I16   |      2^20      |   3.995 us |       7.15% |   3.985 us |       6.70% |  -0.010 us |  -0.26% |   SAME   |\r\n|   I16   |      2^24      |  18.979 us |       4.67% |  16.848 us |       5.17% |  -2.131 us | -11.23% |   FAST   |\r\n|   I16   |      2^28      | 316.365 us |       0.33% | 318.232 us |       0.46% |   1.867 us |   0.59% |   SLOW   |\r\n|   I32   |      2^16      |   3.892 us |      12.23% |   3.565 us |      22.78% |  -0.327 us |  -8.39% |   SAME   |\r\n|   I32   |      2^20      |   4.061 us |       8.60% |   4.054 us |       8.47% |  -0.007 us |  -0.17% |   SAME   |\r\n|   I32   |      2^24      |  37.647 us |       2.63% |  37.364 us |       2.47% |  -0.283 us |  -0.75% |   SAME   |\r\n|   I32   |      2^28      | 637.419 us |       0.31% | 636.278 us |       0.36% |  -1.141 us |  -0.18% |   SAME   |\r\n|   I64   |      2^16      |   3.953 us |       7.35% |   3.954 us |       7.31% |   0.000 us |   0.01% |   SAME   |\r\n|   I64   |      2^20      |   6.021 us |       4.25% |   6.027 us |       4.23% |   0.005 us |   0.09% |   SAME   |\r\n|   I64   |      2^24      |  77.893 us |       1.04% |  77.498 us |       1.14% |  -0.394 us |  -0.51% |   SAME   |\r\n|   I64   |      2^28      |   1.279 ms |       0.33% |   1.278 ms |       0.19% |  -1.119 us |  -0.09% |   SAME   |\r\n```",
